$ icacls.exe

Manage *discretionary access control lists* (DACL) on files and directories.

`icacls.exe` is newer than → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cacls_exe[`cacls.exe`]

Some abbreviations are:
  • `OI`: Object inherit
  • `CI`: Container inherit
  • `F`: Full control

In → Windows/PowerShell, there is also the → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/acl/get[cmdlet `get-acl`].

code {
icacls C:\Windows\SysWOW64\d3d9.dll /grant *S-1-5-32-544:F
code }

sa:

  → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/acl

  The → Windows/tools/Sysinternals tool → Windows/tools/Sysinternals/AccessChk[AccessChk].
